data.description: Out of the pages of a design magazine & packed with upgrades! Updates include hand-scrapped hardwood flrs; an ultra-modern kitchen w granite & SS appls, oven, vent, & microwave 2021. Bathrms have easy-care tile floors & trendy mirrors. The primary BR has ensuite w separate vanities, walk-in shower, & barn door leading to commode. Two more sets of barn doors add an element of whimsey to this heart-stealing home. Sunlight infused den has added charm with a German smeared FP & white washed walls. Secondary LR could be formal dining or office. Bkyd is a delight w huge trees, deck, & new spa, 8 seat hot tub 2020 with an added electrical box 2020. Storage shed & newly built covd work area . Additional upgrades: water heater 2021, 8' fence 2020, HVAC 2018, garage dr opener 2020, electrical panel 2020, radiant barrier & extra attic insulation, water heater 2021, exterior painted & gutters added 2021, chimney cap & gutter guards, French drain in front and backyard 2021. A rare property!
